<subSubSection pageId="2" pageNumber="487" type="diagnosis">
<paragraph blockId="2.[159,781,662,1163]" pageId="2" pageNumber="487">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[159,275,758,781]" pageId="2" pageNumber="487">Diagnosis.</emphasis>
The species may be differentiated from other members of the 
<taxonomicName baseAuthorityName="Walch" baseAuthorityYear="1775" box="[339,554,790,813]" class="Insecta" family="Hesperiidae" genus="Astraptes" kingdom="Animalia" order="Lepidoptera" pageId="2" pageNumber="487" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="fulgerator">
<emphasis box="[339,554,790,813]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="487">Astraptes fulgerator</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
complex by the following combination of character states of the DNA barcode: 38 
<collectionCode box="[250,268,854,877]" name="Tavera, Department of Geology and Geophysics" pageId="2" pageNumber="487">T</collectionCode>
; 52 
<collectionCode box="[306,323,854,877]" name="Tavera, Department of Geology and Geophysics" pageId="2" pageNumber="487">T</collectionCode>
; 202 
<collectionCode box="[376,393,854,877]" name="Tavera, Department of Geology and Geophysics" pageId="2" pageNumber="487">T</collectionCode>
; 205C; 274 
<collectionCode box="[516,533,854,877]" name="Tavera, Department of Geology and Geophysics" pageId="2" pageNumber="487">T</collectionCode>
; 568A. 202 
<collectionCode box="[655,671,854,877]" name="Tavera, Department of Geology and Geophysics" pageId="2" pageNumber="487">T</collectionCode>
and 568A are unique fixed states for 
<taxonomicName authorityName="BROWER" authorityYear="2010" box="[449,548,885,908]" class="Insecta" family="Hesperiidae" genus="Astraptes" kingdom="Animalia" order="Lepidoptera" pageId="2" pageNumber="487" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="favilla">
<emphasis box="[449,548,885,908]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="487">A. favilla</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
with respect to other members of the 
<taxonomicName baseAuthorityName="Walch" baseAuthorityYear="1775" box="[330,466,917,940]" class="Insecta" family="Hesperiidae" genus="Astraptes" kingdom="Animalia" order="Lepidoptera" pageId="2" pageNumber="487" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="fulgerator">
<emphasis box="[330,466,917,940]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="487">A. fulgerator</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
complex.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
